# DOWNLOAD

- Link for people who downloading by internet browser:

http://github.com/webnull/OpenWikiBlog/zipball/master

- Commands to type in SSH (Terminal) to download OpenWikiBlog framework:

wget http://github.com/webnull/OpenWikiBlog/zipball/master --no-check-certificate -O OpenWikiBlog.zip
unzip OpenWikiBlog.zip
rm OpenWikiBlog.zip

# INSTALLATION

- When you downloaded copy of OpenWikiBlog repository and extracted it now you have to set needed to work chmods (file privileges):

755 - data/crash
755 - data/db
755 - data/templates_c
755 - data/cache
755 - data/cache/kernel
755 - data/tmp

You can do it by your FTP client or by typing these commands in Terminal:

chown www-data data/crash data/db data/templates_c data/tmp data/cache -R
chmod -R 755 data/crash data/db data/templates_c

- Now everything is working and ready to work.
Congratulations.


